{"type":"text","timestamp":1782387078983,"sessionID":"ses_1017781aeffeW652duigCyEXur","part":{"id":"prt_efe8c70bb001OABuel6MFYBnPg","messageID":"msg_efe8c2604001COwnHU3yP5uCDb","sessionID":"ses_1017781aeffeW652duigCyEXur","type":"text","text":"The main evidence points to a router-plus-sibling-family model: `ui-skills-root` explicitly routes to smallest useful contexts, `impeccable` exposes many commands under one broad surface, and `designer-skills-main` uses collections/plugins as modular sibling bundles. I’m writing the lineage artifacts now with a converged loop rather than forcing all 20 iterations.","time":{"start":1782387077307,"end":1782387078981},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0ad10675d5625731016a3d118535e8819791d699211c7b1e6c","phase":"commentary"}}}}
